                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-317-off1733 t18300415-317-cd1734"></join>, 1 waistcoat, value 2s.; 1<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183004150137"></xptr>handkerchief, value 6d., and 1 comb, value 2d.
